= class GLib::FilesystemPreviewType

Indicates a hint from the file system whether files should be previewed in a
file manager. Returned as the value of the key
GLib::FileAttribute::FILESYSTEM_USE_PREVIEW. 

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Enum
    * GLib::FilesystemPreviewType

== Constants

--- IF_ALWAYS

     Only preview files if user has explicitly requested it

--- IF_LOCAL

     Preview files if user has requested preview of “local” files

--- NEVER

     Never preview files

